text: "Headlong" is a 1991 song by Queen (band) and taken from their 14th studio album Innuendo. It went to number 14 in the United Kingdom and number 25 in Canada and Ireland. It did not chart in the United States. ==Track listings== * 7-inch single :A. "Headlong" – 4:38 :B.
